最小限に抑えることは、雪国に暮らす方々の生活や社会経済活…", "…ていると認識をしています。こうした雪による被害を最小限に抑えることは、雪国に暮らす方々の生活や社会経済活動を守るための重要な課題であると認識…", "…としましても期待をしたいと思います。そして、期待するとともに、政府としても豪雪地帯対策の推進に今後とも全力で取り組んでまいりたいと考えます。"]}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120815261X00220220224/223", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120815261X00220220224/227", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120815261X00220220224/229", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120815261X00220220224/231", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120815261X00220220224/233", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120815261X00220220224/243", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120815261X00220220224/245", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120815261X00220220224/249", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120815261X00220220224/253", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120815261X00220220224/255", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120815261X00220220224/265", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120815261X00220220224/281", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120815261X00220220224/286", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120815261X00220220224/288", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120815261X00220220224/290", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120815261X00220220224/300", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120815261X00220220224/305", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120815261X00220220224/309", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120815261X00220220224/311", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120815261X00220220224/313", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120815261X00220220224/315", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120815261X00220220224/317", "sente